name: Pardieiro
description:
The idea of seeing my world from the outside was the catalyst for this series, providing the 3D model in a single piece, accompanied by 3 photographs in a series of 13 called "Pardieiro" which the Portuguese to English translation means "Construction old, in disrepair or in ruins".
It was in this space that the idea was born, it will be in the creation that it will stay for eternity!
